    public final class NameRecord
extends ContinuableRecord
    Defines a named range within a workbook.(定义工作簿内的命名范围。)

        Constructor to create a built-in named region(创建内置命名区域的构造器)
        Parameters:
        builtin - Built-in byte representation for the name record, use the public constants(builtin -名称记录的内置字节表示，使用公共常量)
        sheetNumber - the sheet which the name applies to(sheetNumber -名称适用的工作表)
